Carousel
---------------
This is also known as slideshow or image slider .
It is one of the best way of showcasing the huge amount of contents within a small space on the web page.

use carousel class


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Carousel</title>
    <style>
        .carousel-item {
            min-height: 300px;
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
